# Documentation-only repository.
#
# This folder also contains a 7.8 GB disc image, ~36 GB of extracted game
# assets, third-party tools and working code. None of it belongs here, so the
# policy is an allowlist: ignore everything, then re-admit only the docs.

*

!README.md
!LICENSE
!.gitignore
!docs/
!docs/*.md
!docs/*.csv

# Explicitly, never: game data of any kind. Bring your own copy.
*.iso
*.xex
*.xma
*.bnk
*.dds
*.wav
extracted/
preview/
